OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted boss rejects calls  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto pause inspections       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Stopping school inspections in England 
OL,6, would be "against children's best      
OL,7, interests", Ofsted's chief has said.   
OL,9,FTeachers have called for them to be    
OL,10,Fpaused, after head teacher Ruth Perry  
OL,11,Ftook her own life while waiting for a  
OL,12,Freport that downgraded her school from 
OL,13,F"outstanding" to "inadequate".         
OL,15,FAmanda Spielman said inspections are   
OL,16,Fimportant for both schools and parents.
OL,18,FIt comes as the BBC can reveal Ms Perry
OL,19,Fhad been "delighted" with feedback from
OL,20,FOfsted in an informal visit in 2019.   
